description: White Eyes is making its way through every exciting event in the Southwest and serving up deliciously crunchy and fluffy fry bread. This family-run trailer is where you’ll find some of the most flavorful fry bread you may ever try. Their signature dough recipe starts off frozen, but it’s served to you hot, fresh, and fast. You’re free to top your authentic treat with all sorts of tastiness. Ask this team to pile on meat, beans, and veggies, and you’ve got yourself an incredibly scrumptious Indian Taco! For a fabulous dessert, have your fry bread topped with cinnamon sugar or honey or Nutella, (and these are just a few of the yummy choices). For some fantastic fry bread and famously friendly service, be sure to come by White Eyes!
name: White Eyes
